overview.en: FM is a basic setting for building a commercial blockchain. Both companies and individuals can use FM to realize payment, which is easy to operate. FM is a transaction medium between merchants, merchants and individuals, and individuals. FM as a digital currency will fully become a circulation demand and emerge..
overview.zh: FM是构建商业区块链基础设置，无论是企业还是个人都可以使用FM实现支付，操作方便。FM为商家与商家、商家与个体、个体之间交易媒介，FM作为一种数字货币就会充分成为流通需求而出现。
